DESCRIPTION_COPY: Kopisha konke okubiningeni ukususa kubhodi yokukopisha.
DESCRIPTION_EXPORT: Londoloza konke izinto kususini ukuya ku-fayela .json.
DESCRIPTION_IMPORT: Bechanjela zonke izinto kwi-trashbin ngaphandle kwe-fayela ye-.json.
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_ENABLED: Isilungiso esigcwele sokuvula noma kuvimba konke okusebenza kweTrashbin+
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_SHOW_WIDGET: Bonisa ikhona yekhobhoza emshinelweni wokudlala ekugcineni umlando okudlalwayo ngoku ngoku ukuze kutholakale kakhudlwana
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_AUTOPLAY: Qala ukudlala imiziki ngokuzenzekelayo xa i-Spotify ivulwe noma isiphindelelo sifaka
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_QUEUE_TRASHBIN: Faka izithombe zedolobha ezinguqu ezinye ngasinye kumculo wakho okulandelako ukuze kube lula ukuphatha
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRACKLIST_TRASHBIN: Faka izithombe zedolobha ezindaweni zomculo kumzobo nomhawu wokudlala ukuze kudlulwe ngokushesha
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_PLAYLIST_MONITOR: Duthukuthe ngokuzenzakalelayo kusiphephe sokudlala kukaSpotify ngokubuyisela kusiphephe sakho sokugcina
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_SKIP_TRASHED_TRACKS: Hhanya ngokuzenzakalelayo izindima ezithunyelwe kususini futhi uthole indima engavumelekile ekulandelweni
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_AUTO_CLEAN_QUEUE: Susa ngokuzenzekala izindima ezithunyelwe ku-Smart Shuffle queue yakho
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRASH_ON_NEXT_HOTKE: Cindeza ngokuzenzakalelayo imibhalo yamanje xa usebenzisa u-Ctrl+Right ukuthi uphumelela kumusindo olandelayo
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_REMOTE_TOGGLE: Cindeza kabili ukudlala/ukumisa ukumisa ukungena kwe-remote kumashtuli. Ukungena kumgwaqo kuthola ukuthi kucindezelwe.
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_REMOTE_SKIPPING: Xa kusekelwe, ukungahleli kusebenza noma kube wawusebenzisa i-Spotify kusihlangothi sesinye (umzekelo, ihhandi)
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRASH_VIA_LIKE: Njengomculo okuthuthelwa ku-trash. Ukuthanda kususwa ngokuzenzekala futhi kuhambela umculo olandelayo.
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_AI_DETECTION_ENABLE: Lethola imiziki engenisiwe ngu-AI usebenzisa imodeli ye-SONICS bese ubonisa ubukhona besimo. Liphakelisa imodeli engu-50MB ngokuqala ukuba kusebenze.
DESCRIPTION_SETTINGS_TRASH_AI_SONGS: Cindezela ngokuzenzakalelayo izindima ezitholakala njengokuthi zidolenzelwe yi-AI (imiphikiswano â‰¥ 80%)
